text: Erdem Onur Beytaş (born 30 April 1998 in Melikgazi, Turkey) is a Turkish footballer who plays as a midfielder for Belediye Kütahyaspor on loan from Ankara Keçiörengücü.https://twitter.com/MemleketLigleri/status/1310929067349286912 Erdem Onur made his professional debut with Kayserispor in a 5-0 loss to İstanbul Başakşehir on 14 January 2017. ==References== == External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kayseri Category:Turkish footballers Category:Kayserispor footballers Category:Süper Lig players Category:Association football midfielders
